---
title: Pork & Creamy Garlic-Chive Sauce with Parmesan Fries
description: We're not going to lie – this creamy sauce is so good you'll want to slather it over everything! Here, we've teamed it with tender
pork loin steaks, pan-fried veggies and moreish Parmesan fries.

